text: Marie-Odile Bouillé Marie-Odile Bouillé (born October 13, 1950 in Nantes) is a member of the National Assembly of France. She represents the Loire-Atlantique department, and is a member of the Socialiste, radical, citoyen et divers gauche. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:People from Nantes Category:Socialist Party (France) politicians Category:Women members of the National Assembly (France) Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:21st-century French women politicians
